OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FRyanair has adjusted its family
OL,8,Fseating policy after an investigation
OL,9,Fwas opened into it charging parents to
OL,10,Fsit with their young children on
OL,11,Fflights.
OL,13,FAdults who do not wish to pay for a
OL,14,Freserved seat next to them will now be
OL,15,Ftold of their free seat allocation
OL,16,Fafter check-in.
OL,18,FAirline boss Michael O'Leary said it
OL,19,Fwould "reluctantly adjust to this
OL,20,Findustry standard".
OL,26,@{D@GOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
