CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FThe "minor policy tweak" came into
OL,8,Feffect on Thursday.
OL,10,FSo-called "free parent seats" will now
OL,11,Fbe available at the back of the
OL,12,Faircraft, as front rows tend to be
OL,13,Freserved.
OL,15,FEarlier this month, the Competition
OL,16,Fand Markets Authority (CMA) watchdog
OL,17,Flaunched a probe to determine whether
OL,18,FRyanair's policy at the time was "in
OL,19,Fline with consumer law".
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@XO]rD@KOUrD@]O]zD@bOU{D@WO]
