FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FRyanair previously required parents
OL,8,Ftravelling with children aged between
OL,9,Ftwo and 11 to pay to reserve what it
OL,10,Freferred to as a mandatory family seat.
OL,12,FTheir children were then allocated
OL,13,Fseats next to or near them free of
OL,14,Fcharge.
OL,16,FThe fee for a mandatory family seat
OL,17,Fwas typically about #8 each way, the
OL,18,FCMA said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
