CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FUnder the new policy, parents will
OL,8,Fstill have the option of paying to
OL,9,Freserve a seat of their choosing and
OL,10,Fhave their children alongside them
OL,11,Ffree of charge.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
