OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FChief executive Mr O'Leary accused the
OL,8,FCMA of "turning a blind eye" to the
OL,9,F"high fares" charged by airlines on
OL,10,Froutes with no competition from the
OL,11,FDublin-based carrier.
OL,13,FHe said: "The CMA has now targeted our
OL,14,Ffamily seating policy which has been
OL,15,Funiversally embraced by consumers as
OL,16,Fthe most progressive and transparent
OL,17,Fin Europe.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@\O]qD@AOUqD@LO]uD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"Instead of promoting competitiveness
OL,8,Fand lower fares for consumers, the CMA
OL,9,Fis on a mission to force Ryanair to
OL,10,Fadopt the less transparent and less
OL,11,Fconsumer-friendly family seating
OL,12,Fpolicy applied by most other airlines
OL,13,F` just because it's the industry
OL,14,Fstandard.
OL,16,F"We will reluctantly adjust to this
OL,17,Findustry standard as we don't want to
OL,18,Fwaste time explaining to misguided
OL,19,Fregulators how badly they
OL,20,Fmisunderstand what is in the best
OL,21,Finterest of UK and Europe's consumers.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"Under our revised family seating
OL,8,Fpolicy, families may have to wait
OL,9,Funtil after they have checked in to
OL,10,Ffind out their seat allocation and are
OL,11,Fmore likely to be seated at the rear
OL,12,Fof the cabin but at least the CMA will
OL,13,Fbe able to claim they have done
OL,14,Fsomething for consumers, but sadly
OL,15,Fmost consumers won't notice."
OL,17,FRyanair said the change will be
OL,18,F"revenue neutral".
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@]O]zD@AOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FRory Boland, editor of consumer
OL,8,Fmagazine Which? Travel, said: "It
OL,9,Fshould never have required Which? to
OL,10,Freport Ryanair's unfair seating policy
OL,11,Fto the CMA to prompt action on these
OL,12,Funjustified charges.
OL,14,F"It was never fair to charge parents
OL,15,Fto sit next to children as young as
OL,16,Fthree.
OL,26,@pD@_OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"It's clear Ryanair is unhappy about
OL,8,Fbeing dragged into doing the right
OL,9,Fthing, so Which? will be monitoring
OL,10,Fthe implications of this policy and
OL,11,Fwhether all parents are seated next to
OL,12,Ftheir children without charge over the
OL,13,Fnext few months."
OL,15,FA CMA spokesperson said: "Ryanair
OL,16,Fclaims its seating policy now complies
OL,17,Fwith the law, and we'll test that
OL,18,Fthoroughly.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@QO]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1782465502
OL,3,C'Reluctant' Ryanair will not charge
OL,4,Cparents to sit next to children on
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,F"If true, it's a win for families `
OL,8,Fwho will no longer have to pay to sit
OL,9,Fwith their children ` and it shows the
OL,10,Fimpact our new powers are having.
OL,12,F"But it doesn't change the fact
OL,13,Ffamilies have been paying for
OL,14,F'mandatory family seats'. Our
OL,15,Finvestigation remains ongoing."
OL,17,FThe CMA said Ryanair's decision to
OL,18,Fchange its policy was made at its own
OL,19,Fdiscretion.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOU
